con:testSuite.name: UpdatePolicyHolder_TestSuite
con:testSuite.con:description:
There are two postive test cases in this test suite for Asyn service for change policy holder.
Add policy holder as bulk. First, create two polices. Second, add 'SMOKE002' as a new BP for the first policy; add "Z" as as a new BP for the second policy. Third, read the first policy to check the change; read the second policy to check the change.
Modify delete policy holder as bulk. First, modify the main BP for the first policy from 'SMOKE001' to 'Z'. Second, delete the non-main BP 'Z'. for the second policy. Third, read the first policy to check the change; read the second policy to check the change.

AddPolicyHolderAsBulk_Positive
